6. EXPERIMENTAL EVALUATION

6.1 Emulator Setup

We developed CXL-Sim-FM, a high-fidelity CXL fabric emulator in Python (8 ports, 4 VCSs, 16 DCD extents, full FMAPI). While not hardware, it implements the exact spec logic—demonstrating that attacks are architectural, not implementation bugs.

Why emulation suffices: Our TLA+ proof shows attacks are spec-permitted. Emulation confirms they are executable. Hardware would add latency numbers but not change the security conclusion.

